	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey gang... at 59 you are able to Solo the guardian camp in seb,....Huge money maker. <br><br>Catch is managing your canning with mana ratio.... never go below 50% health... keep regrowth on. Screw resist gear and ac gear... pack on mana gear.<br><br>with Bane of Nife, Pox and JBB to nuke there isnt much you cant handle in Sebs Guardian Camp. <br><br>Pop your pet. Dont bother buffing him, Buff yourself. regrowth is important...and always try to bum a C2 or C3.<br><br>Mem:<br>Bane of Nife, Pox, Slow, Ice Strike/ Cancel Magic, Malo, Root, Sup Healing, and Regrowth.<br>yes 9 listed...swap out icestrike and cancel magic once the the bugs are cleared.<br><br>once your ready, the hard part in single pulling the first scarab... hug the wall as far back as you can while making sure you can see the scarab... cast Cancel Magic...this 9 out of 10 times brings a single scarab... sick pet and root mob... back up and slow it. Now stack your dots... Pox / Bane join in and help your pet... bracer nuking now and then and in short order its dead... woot Blue Diamond! <br><br>anywho many get mad at some of us shaman on Zeb server as a few of us hold this camp alone and solo it well... catch is if they want your camp badly enough they can train you easy... once that happens your screwed... Run to exit, cause you wont have time to mem Gate.<br><br>In 3 hours i walked out of Seb with 3800 plat.. + a ton of gems and crowns as well as one lammy and a mask... the gems and diamonds/blue Diamonds sell for high plat once you CHA buff yourself.<br><br>3 hour end total = 11,133pp... why bother counting the copper and silver..(destroy)<br><br>Please feel free to send me a tell and i'll be happy to let ya sit in for a free ride to learn how its done. Im EST and if i can get the guardian camp its usually around 3am - 5am EST.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Gillianna<br>63 Barbarian Shamanistical Fantastica<br>www.noctuserus.com<br>Zebuxoruk Server<br>Smoke'n me Peace Pipe Since '99 don'tcha know<br><br></td></tr>
