	   <tr><td colspan=2>I recall at level 10 going to the skeleton fort in Nektulous Forrest to the right as you zone in from EC--the sell the stacks of bonechips for 5-10pp per stack. Another good way is to get about 30pp and master pottery ( yes it can be done that cheap ) and make +2 WIS range dieties for clerics and druids--you can get between 50-100pp for each of these. The sand of Ro that u need to make them only drops from sand giants but alot of people will give them away or charge 10pp each at the most--i made over 4kpp selling these in my early days as a young ogre shaman. Hope this helps ya.<br><br>53 Ogre BattleMystic on Luclin sever--Aggrok<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
