	   <tr><td colspan=2>I left EQ a bit back and when I came back I started playing on FV, then moved to the legends server when it came out. I can't stand not having a little red in my eq so I'm making an alt on rallos. Ive decided to go with an Iksar Shaman. I was wondering if anyone knows of any quests or drops I could easily get that are no drop at my level(think 9+). Also, any advice would be helpful, I never played a shaman. Picked one for teh DoTs and nice buffs. <br>&nbsp;<br>-------------------------<br>Ababar<br>22 Gnome Wizard<br>Rallos Zek Server</td></tr>
